\u2013359|doi=10.15184/aqy.2017.21|issn=0003-598X|ref=harv|via=}}\n* {{cite journal |last1=Jeong |first1=Choongwon |author-link1= |date=November 27, 2018 |editor1-last= |editor1-first= |editor1-link= |title=Bronze Age population dynamics and the rise of dairy pastoralism on the eastern Eurasian steppe |script-title= |trans-title= |department= |journal=[[Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America]] |type= |series= |language= |edition= |publisher=[[National Academy of Sciences]] |publication-date= |volume= 115|issue= 48|pages=966\u2013976 |nopp= |arxiv= |asin= |bibcode= |bibcode-access= |biorxiv= |citeseerx=  |doi=10.1073/pnas.1813608115 |doi-access= |issn= |jfm= |jstor= |jstor-access= |lccn= |mr= |oclc= |ol= |ol-access= |osti= |osti-access= |pmc=6275519 |pmid=30397125 |rfc= |ssrn= |zbl= |id= |layurl= |laysource= |laydate= |quote= |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite journal |last1=Jeong |first1=Choongwon |author-link1= |date=April 29, 2019 |editor1-last= |editor1-first= |editor1-link= |title=The genetic history of admixture across inner Eurasia languages in Europe |script-title= |trans-title= |department= |journal=[[Nature Ecology and Evolution]] |type= |series= |language= |edition= |publisher=[[Nature Research]] |publication-date= |volume=3 |issue= 6|pages=966\u2013976 |nopp= |arxiv= |asin= |bibcode= |bibcode-access= |biorxiv= |citeseerx=  |doi=10.1038/s41559-019-0878-2 |doi-access= |issn= |jfm= |jstor= |jstor-access= |lccn= |mr= |oclc= |ol= |ol-access= |osti= |osti-access= |pmc=6542712 |pmid=31036896 |rfc= |ssrn= |zbl= |id= |layurl= |laysource= |laydate= |quote= |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite journal |last1=Jones |first1=Eppie R. |author-link1= |date=November 16, 2015 |editor1-last= |editor1-first= |editor1-link= |title=Upper Palaeolithic genomes reveal deep roots of modern Eurasians |script-title= |trans-title= |department= |journal=[[Nature Communications]] |type= |series= |language= |edition= |publisher=[[Nature Research]] |publication-date= |volume